Template: ossec-hids-agent/enable_email
Type: string
Default: yes
Description: If we want to send alerts by email
  (else it is just stored in /var/ossec/logs)

Template: ossec-hids-agent/email_to
Type: string
Default: root@localhost
Description: The email to send alerts to
 This is the general email where alerts will be sent to.
 For finer grain, you can add other specific rules inside the ossec.conf file

Template: ossec-hids-agent/email_from
Type: string
Default: ossecm@ossec.server
Description: The email origin from
 This is the email adress where alerts will come from.

Template: ossec-hids-agent/email_server
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: smtp server address (name or ip)

Template: ossec-hids-agent/enable_syslog
Type: string
Default: no
Description: send also via syslog

